model.administration - package model.administration

Model classes for the administrative functions of the Grader tool, including managing the user database and user permissions.

model.announcements - package model.announcements

Model classes for the teacher-student communication functionalities of the Grader tool, including announcement posting and assignment viewing/turn-in.

model.curve - package model.curve

Model classes for the curve manipulation and calculation for the Grader tool, including adding new grade scales to the curve.

model.driver - package model.driver

Models the main class of the Grader tool, which stores all the information regarding the current roster and possible rosters and interfaces with the GUI.

model.graph - package model.graph

Model classes for drawing and manipulating the graphs in the Grader tool, such as the histogram and pie chart representing the class curve and line graphs representing grade trends over time.

model.history - package model.history

Model classes for the history functionality of the Grader tool, storing previous classes and calculating trends across previous iterations of the course.

model.predictions - package model.predictions

Model classes for the grade-prediction functionalities of the Grader tool, for both instructors and students.

model.roster - package model.roster

Model classes for the class management aspects of the Grader tool.

model.server - package model.server

This package contains all the java classes related to running our simulated polylearn server.
